A mere ‘thank you’ is an understatement for the selflessness, generosity and devotion you show our family each and every day... 
Love you to bits! ♥️😘

column1:
As we usher in 2018 with renewed enthusiasm, let's reminisce about the year gone by, learn from its lessons and thank God for all the precious blessings HE has bestowed upon us. 

May 2018 be loaded with peace, joy and prosperity, and may it bring good tidings to everyone! 😍

Celebrating my 21st birthday with my unsurpassed boss and precious teammates at my second home... ❤️🎉🎈
What an uplifting start for my new year! 😍

Happy birthday to the person who has meticulously and extensively taught me! 
Among the manifold skills you possess, I certainly admire your leadership qualities which are conspicuous, for you have inspired  multiple generations and people, including me. Definitely, you have got the gift of the gab!
I owe you more than I can ever repay. 
May you reap the reward of your diligence and dedication, and may you always be my mentor!
Have a flourishing year... ❤️❤️

الشخص "الوحيد" اللي يستحق الواحد يفضي مساحة من وقته و يعقد يتفرج عليه بتركيز و تأمل. ثقافة بلا حدود ... تحليل منطقى ... جرأه ... غير متلون ... مش مطبلاتي ... و كل ده كفيل انه يقعده فى البيت - لو مكنش فى السجن - فى ظل العصر الذي نعيشه. "ففى الوقت الذى ساهم فيه فى اتساع عقول، تسبب كذلك فى ضيق صدور."
بدل ما توقف برنامج، ناقش اللي بيقوله و كدبه و طلعه غلط لكن لا احد يجرأ يعمل كده فى مصر لانكوا اضعف من كده. 
شكرا ابراهيم عيسي و الحق حتما سينتصر...

As every end marks a new beginning, keep your spirits and determination unshaken. With faith, perseverance and hard work, we can accomplish everything we crave. 
May 2017 be filled with blessings to the brim... 🙏🙏
